---
import "../styles/RRGroup-estilos.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html class="scroll-smooth [scroll-padding-top:50px]">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Distribución estratégica en Paraguay - RR Group"
		/>
		<title>RRGroup</title>
		<link rel="icon" href="/Icono_RRGroup.ico" />
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
		/>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
	</head>
	<body class="font-body">
		<div id="intro" class="flex fixed top-0 left-0 w-screen h-screen bg-white justify-center items-center z-2000">
			<img id="intro-logo" class="w-[300px] h-auto" src="/Logo_RRGroup.png" alt="Logo RRGroup"/>
		</div>
		<header id="header" class="sticky top-0 z-[1000] bg-brand-dark gap-10 py-2.5 shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
			<div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-5 flex items-center justify-between">
				<img id="logo"
  class="w-[120px] h-auto block m-0 transition-all duration-300 brightness-0 invert hover:scale-105 hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_#6f6f6f]"
  src="/Logo_RRGroup.png" alt="Logotipo"/>
				<div id="menu-toggle"><i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i></div>
				<nav id="nav-links" aria-label="Menú principal">
					<a href="#hero">Inicio</a>
					<a href="#sobre_nosotros">Sobre Nosotros </a>
					<a href="#mision"> Misión</a>
					<a href="#vision"> Visión</a>
					<a href="#porque_elegirnos"> Porque Elegirnos</a>
					<a href="#marcas"> Marcas con las que trabajamos</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>
		<section id="hero" class=" h-[70vh] bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)),url('/Hero.jpg')] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white text-center m-0">
			<h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Conectamos marcas con el mercado Paraguayo</h1>
			<p class="text-xl mb-8">Distribución estratégica y confiable para cada negocio</p>
			<a href="#contactar" class="bg-brand-red text-white no-underline px-[35px] py-[15px] rounded-[30px] font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-brand-blue hover:scale-105">Contactanos</a>
		</section>
		<section id="sobre_nosotros"
  class="bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/sobre-nosotros.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat my-[50px] mx-auto text-white rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 px-5 py-[60px] shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] max-w-site hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.02] hover:grayscale">
			<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Sobre nosotros</h2>
			<p>
				RR GROUP E.A.S fue formado con una visión preponderante hacia el
				mercado paraguayo. Buscamos innovarlo continuamente con una
				eficaz incorporación de productos altamente rentables. Apuntamos
				a ser distribuidor oficial de empresas destinadas a la venta
				directa al público final. Nuestra modalidad se basa, en crear un
				vínculo confiable y profesional con nuestros clientes; logrando
				así; una experiencia apta, rentable y duradera en cada negocio,
				coordinando en cada operación los puntos más importantes de la
				logística comercial.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section id="mision"
  class="bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/mision.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat my-[50px] mx-auto text-white text-left rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 px-5 py-[60px] shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] max-w-site hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.02] hover:grayscale">
			<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Misión</h2>
			<p>
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Animi
				voluptate incidunt iste optio maxime nobis ex voluptatem, quae
				ipsum ea et alias, repellat, autem saepe inventore eligendi
				laborum iure explicabo.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section id="vision"
  class="bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/vision.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat my-[50px] mx-auto text-white text-left rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 px-5 py-[60px] shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] max-w-site hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.02] hover:grayscale">
			<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Visión</h2>
			<p>
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Atque
				nobis quas distinctio ratione nesciunt doloribus quasi id illo
				delectus praesentium est nemo harum, veritatis sequi dolores
				nam, esse ut recusandae.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section id="porque_elegirnos" class="max-w-site mx-auto my-[50px] px-5 py-[60px] rounded-xl shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
			<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Porque elegirnos</h2>
			<ul class="list-none flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-[30px] m-0 p-0">
				<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-white p-[50px] rounded-xl text-center flex-[1_1_50px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:grayscale
        bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/li-1.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
					Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit
					amet, consectetur, adipisci velit...
				</li>
				<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-white p-[50px] rounded-xl text-center flex-[1_1_50px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:grayscale
        bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/li-2.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
					Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit
					amet, consectetur, adipisci velit...
				</li>
				<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-white p-[50px] rounded-xl text-center flex-[1_1_50px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:grayscale
        bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/li-3.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
					Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit
					amet, consectetur, adipisci velit...
				</li>
				<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] text-white p-[50px] rounded-xl text-center flex-[1_1_50px] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[5px] hover:scale-[1.03] hover:grayscale
        bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),url('/li-4.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center">
					Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit
					amet, consectetur, adipisci velit...
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		<section id="marcas" class="relative overflow-hidden flex flex-wrap flex-col justify-center max-w-site mx-auto my-[50px] px-5 py-[60px] gap-[30px]">
			<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center w-full">Marcas con las que trabajamos</h2>
			<div id="marca-track" class="flex gap-[30px] m-0">
				<a href="https://thonet-vander.com" target="_blank">
					<img class="block border-2 border-black rounded-full w-[240px] h-[240px] object-contain transition-[scale,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-[0_8px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]" src="/Logo_Thonet_Vander.webp" alt="Thonet Vander"  />
				</a>
				<a href="https://devia.com.py" target="_blank">
					<img class="block border-2 border-black rounded-full w-[240px] h-[240px] object-contain transition-[scale,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-[0_8px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]" src="/Logo_Devia.webp" alt="Devia" />
				</a>
				<a href="https://robotloona.com.py" target="_blank">
					<img class="block border-2 border-black rounded-full w-[240px] h-[240px] object-contain transition-[scale,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-[0_8px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]" src="/Logo_Robot_Loona.avif" alt="RobotLoona"/>
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/ecovers.py/" target="_blank">
					<img class="block border-2 border-black rounded-full w-[240px] h-[240px] object-contain transition-[scale,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-[0_8px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]" src="/Logo_Ecovers.jpg" alt="Ecovers"/>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="contactar" class="flex justify-between items-start gap-[40px] max-w-site mx-auto my-[50px] px-5 py-[60px] rounded-xl shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]">
			<div id="datos" class="flex-1 bg-white text-black p-[70px] rounded-xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Contactos</h2>
				<p>
					<i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Ubicación: Asunción,
					Paraguay
				</p>
				<p>
					<i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> Teléfono: +595 983 123456
				</p>
				<p>
					<i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Email: contacto@gmail.com
				</p>
			</div>
			<div id="contactanos" class="flex-1 bg-[#f3f3f3] rounded-xl">
				<h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl text-center">Contáctanos</h2>
				<form action="#" method="post" class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-5">
					<label for="nombre">Nombre completo:</label>
					<input class="w-full max-w-[400px] p-2 bg-white border border-red-500 rounded-xl text-base outline-none transition-all duration-300 focus:border-brand-red focus:shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(255,60,60,0.4)]" type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" required />
					<label for="email">Email:</label>
					<input class="w-full max-w-[400px] p-2 bg-white border border-red-500 rounded-xl text-base outline-none transition-all duration-300 focus:border-brand-red focus:shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(255,60,60,0.4)]" type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
					<label for="telefono">Teléfono:</label>
					<input class="w-full max-w-[400px] p-2 bg-white border border-red-500 rounded-xl text-base outline-none transition-all duration-300 focus:border-brand-red focus:shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(255,60,60,0.4)]" type="tel" id="telefono" name="telefono" required />
					<label for="mensaje">Mensaje:</label>
					<textarea class="w-full max-w-[400px] p-2 bg-white border border-red-500 rounded-xl text-base outline-none transition-all duration-300 focus:border-brand-red focus:shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(255,60,60,0.4)]" id="mensaje" name="mensaje" required></textarea>
					<button class="bg-brand-red text-white px-5 py-2.5 mb-2.5 rounded-[20px] font-semibold transition-all duration-300 border-none cursor-pointer hover:bg-brand-blue hover:scale-105" type="submit">Enviar</button>
				</form>
			</div>
		</section>
		<footer id="contacto" class="bg-brand-dark text-white px-5 pt-[60px] pb-5">
			<div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-5 flex flex-wrap items-start gap-[40px] justify-between" id="footer-container">
				<div id="footer-col-1" class="flex-[1_1_220px]">
					<img src="/Logo_RRGroup.png" alt="Logo" id="footer-logo" class="w-[120px] mb-4 brightness-0 invert" />
					<p class="text-white text-[0.95rem]">
						Conectamos marcas con el mercado paraguayo mediante
						distribución estratégica y confiable.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div id="footer-col-2" class="flex-[1_1_220px]">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-brand-red">Enlaces</h3>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#hero">Inicio</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#sobre_nosotros">Sobre Nosotros</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#mision">Misión</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#vision">Visión</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#porque_elegirnos">Porque elegirnos</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#marcas">Marcas con las que trabajamos</a>
					<a class="block text-white no-underline mb-2 transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-x-[5px]" href="#contactar">Contactar</a>
				</div>
				<div id="footer-col-3" class="flex-[1_1_220px]">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-brand-red">Contacto</h3>
					<p class="text-white text-[0.95rem]">
						<i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
						Asunción, Paraguay
					</p>
					<p class="text-white text-[0.95rem]">
						<i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> +595 983 123456
					</p>
					<p class="text-white text-[0.95rem]">
						<i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> contacto@gmail.com
					</p>
				</div>
				<div id="footer-col-4" class="flex-[1_1_220px] flex flex-col items-center">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-brand-red">Seguinos</h3>
					<div class="social-icons">
						<a class="text-2xl text-brand-red no-underline transition-all duration-300 hover:text-white hover:scale-125" href="https://www.facebook.com" target="_blank">
							<i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
						</a>
						<a class="text-2xl text-brand-red no-underline transition-all duration-300 hover:text-white hover:scale-125" href="https://www.instagram.com" target="_blank">
							<i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="w-full border-t border-white pt-[30px] mt-5">
				<div id="footer-bottom-text" class="text-[0.9rem] text-left text-white md:pl-[120px] m-0">
					<p>&copy; 2026 RRGroup - Todos los derechos reservados</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<script src="../scripts/RRGroup-scripts.js"></script>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
